
Define the acceptance criteria (AC) for the core functionality of the app.

	Given user is on book search app home page
	When user search for book with key word
	Then search results displayed

	Given user is search results page
	And user click on any search result
	Then user see the book details (Author, Book Name, Published By)


	Given user is search results page
	And user click on any search result
	Then user see the book details
	And user can share it